              </nav>
            </div>
          </div>

    <main>
        <div class="inner cover">
          <h2> What is #projectdare? </h2>

          <p> It is a game where the risky humans of the Earth choose to do something fun with their lives. </p>

            <ol class="inner cover"> 
              <p id = "step1"> 1. Sign up with Twitter! <i class="fa fa-twitter" style="font-size:32px;color:#33F9FF"></i></p>
              <p id = "step2"> 2. Choose from the list of Dares provided by the community </p>
              <p id = "step3"> 3. Record yourself doing the dare on Twitter and hashtag #ProjectDare</p>
              <p id = "step4"> 4. Enjoy your accomplishment! </p>
            </ol>
        </div>

      <!-- Twitter popup. Hidden when loaded, shows when user clicks on signup/login -->
      <div class="modal fade bd-example-modal-sm" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="mySmallModalLabel" aria-hidden="true" style="padding-top: 20%;">
